It is possible to park a car at the house for free. 

Excellent surrounding infrastructure - there is a Lidl supermarket nearby, also a Rimi Mini supermarket, a post office, a pharmacy, a Maxima supermarket, various educational institutions and other socially important objects are within walking distance. 7 minutes drive to IKEA and s/c Saga. Public bus stops are a 2-minute walk away. 

